{{Actor| | type = SFX | name = ZArmorChunk | class = ZArmorChunk | game = Hexen }}[[Classes]]: <u>ZArmorChunk</u>
An armor piece that is spawned when a {{Class|ZSuitOfArmor|suit of armor}} is smashed.
